Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/jventer/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Git submodule add instructions

    git submodule add https//<giturl> bundle/<localname>

Init and update submodules used for managing plugins

    git submodule init
    git submodule update
